---
title: BeaconLink Job State Machine
---

stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    %% =====================================================
    %% Job Creation
    %% =====================================================

    [*] --> Created

    Created : Job Requested
    Created : Job ID Assigned
    Created : Immutable Specification Stored
    Created : Metadata Persisted

    Created --> PendingValidation

    %% =====================================================
    %% Validation Phase
    %% =====================================================

    PendingValidation : Validate Job Definition
    PendingValidation : Validate Parameters
    PendingValidation : Validate Resources

    PendingValidation --> PolicyEvaluation : Validation Successful
    PendingValidation --> Failed : Validation Failed

    PolicyEvaluation : Evaluate RBAC
    PolicyEvaluation : Evaluate Compliance
    PolicyEvaluation : Evaluate Execution Policies

    PolicyEvaluation --> Scheduling : Authorized
    PolicyEvaluation --> Rejected : Policy Denied

    Rejected : Job Rejected
    Rejected : Await User Correction

    Rejected --> [*]

    %% =====================================================
    %% Scheduling Phase
    %% =====================================================

    Scheduling : Discover Eligible Agents
    Scheduling : Evaluate Runtime Capabilities
    Scheduling : Reserve Execution Capacity

    Scheduling --> Queued : Capacity Reserved
    Scheduling --> Waiting : No Capacity

    Waiting : Await Available Resources

    Waiting --> Scheduling : Resources Available
    Waiting --> Cancelled : Cancel Requested

    %% =====================================================
    %% Queue Lifecycle
    %% =====================================================

    Queued : Await Execution Window
    Queued : Priority Ordering

    Queued --> Dispatching

    %% =====================================================
    %% Dispatch Phase
    %% =====================================================

    Dispatching : Send Job to BeaconLink Agent
    Dispatching : Transfer Immutable Specification
    Dispatching : Establish Execution Context

    Dispatching --> Preparing

    %% =====================================================
    %% Runtime Execution
    %% =====================================================

    state Executing {

        [*] --> Initializing

        Initializing : Resolve Secrets
        Initializing : Download Artifacts
        Initializing : Prepare Runtime
        Initializing : Allocate Resources

        Initializing --> Running

        Running : Execute Job Logic
        Running : Stream Logs
        Running : Publish Metrics

        Running --> Checkpointing : Periodic Checkpoint
        Running --> Suspending : Pause Requested
        Running --> Retrying : Recoverable Failure
        Running --> Verifying : Execution Finished
        Running --> Failed : Fatal Runtime Error

        Checkpointing : Persist Progress
        Checkpointing : Save Execution State

        Checkpointing --> Running

        Suspending : Preserve Runtime Context

        Suspending --> Running : Resume Requested
        Suspending --> Cancelled : Cancel Requested

        Retrying : Apply Retry Policy
        Retrying : Exponential Backoff

        Retrying --> Running
        Retrying --> Failed : Retry Limit Exceeded

        Verifying : Validate Exit Status
        Verifying : Verify Outputs
        Verifying : Collect Final Metrics

        Verifying --> Completed : Success
        Verifying --> Failed : Verification Failed

    }

    Preparing --> Executing

    %% =====================================================
    %% Completion
    %% =====================================================

    Completed : Job Successful
    Completed : Publish Completion Event
    Completed : Persist Results

    Completed --> Archived

    Archived : Immutable Job History
    Archived : Audit Complete

    Archived --> [*]

    %% =====================================================
    %% Failure Recovery
    %% =====================================================

    Failed : Job Failed
    Failed : Diagnostics Available
    Failed : Await Decision

    Failed --> Scheduling : Retry Job
    Failed --> Cancelled : Cancel Job

    %% =====================================================
    %% Cancellation
    %% =====================================================

    Cancelled : Stop Execution
    Cancelled : Release Resources
    Cancelled : Cleanup Secrets
    Cancelled : Notify Workflow

    Cancelled --> Archived

    %% =====================================================
    %% Timeout Handling
    %% =====================================================

    Executing --> TimedOut : Execution Timeout

    TimedOut : Terminate Runtime
    TimedOut : Collect Diagnostics
    TimedOut : Publish Timeout Event

    TimedOut --> Failed

    %% =====================================================
    %% Global Failure Paths
    %% =====================================================

    Scheduling --> Failed : Scheduler Failure
    Dispatching --> Failed : Communication Failure
    Preparing --> Failed : Runtime Initialization Failure
    PendingValidation --> Cancelled : User Cancelled